<m:mi> x </m:mi>
<m:mrow>
<m:mi> C </m:mi>
<m:mi> B </m:mi>
</m:mrow>
</m:msub>
</m:math>
as shown in the figure. The observers are represented by their respective frame of reference in the figure. 
</para>
