<example id="example-23">
<para id="element-23"><term>Problem : </term> Two cars, standing a distance apart, start moving towards each other with speeds 1 m/s and 2 m/s along a straight road. What is the speed with which they approach each other ?
</para>
<para id="element-24"><term>Solution : </term> Let us consider that "A" denotes Earth, "B" denotes first car and "C" denotes second car. The equation of relative velocity for this case is :
</para> 
<para id="element-25">
<m:math display="block">
