<para id="element-40">But we have restricted ourselves to reference systems which are moving at constant velocity. This means that relative velocity of "B" with respect to "A" is a constant. In other words, the acceleration of "B" with respect to "A" is zero i.e. 
<m:math>
<m:msub>
