</m:msub>
</m:math>
" and the other object designated as "2" moves with acceleration "
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> a </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msub>
</m:math>" along a straight line. Then, relative acceleration of "1" with respect to "2" is given by :
</para>
